License: MIT
Description: django-admin-sortable2
        ======================
        
        A replacement for django-admin-sortable using an unintrusive approach.
        
        This plugin is a generic drag-and-drop ordering module for sorting
        objects in the list view of the Django admin interface. It offers simple
        mixin classes which enrich the functionality of any existing class
        derived from ``admin.ModelAdmin``, ``admin.StackedInline`` or
        ``admin.TabluarInline``. Thus it makes it very easy to integrate with
        existing models and their model admin interfaces.
        
        NEW in version 0.3.1
        --------------------
        
        Fixed issue #25 and another small bug.
        
